    "<p class=\"hightlight\"><span class=\"deco\"></span> To form the past participle of <u>regular verbs</u>, add â€“ED to the infinitive: mend<span>ed</span>, clean<span>ed</span>, damag<span>ed</span>. If you do not remember the forms of the irregular verbs, refer to the verb list on the last page of this Manual.</p>",
